Kelp-Module-DBIx-Mint version 0.01
==================================

Welcome to Kelp::Module::DBIx::Mint!

This module will bring a database connection to your Kelp web
application, using DBIx::Mint. DBIx::Mint is an Object-Relational
Mapper.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

* Kelp
* DBIx::Mint

And for testing, DBD::SQLite.

